success or failure.

651
00:48:44,410 --> 00:48:46,330
What good is this to me now?

652
00:48:48,540 --> 00:48:51,400
At least you can explain things clearly
to the girl.

653
00:48:54,630 --> 00:48:56,110
Screw you!

654
