If I die,

655
00:49:11,400 --> 00:49:13,700
you have to let Ji Ya and Duo live.

656
00:49:38,740 --> 00:49:39,789
Ji Ya went to the circulation chamber.

657
00:49:39,790 --> 00:49:40,910
You go get her.

658
00:49:41,840 --> 00:49:44,300
